OL,5,G1900 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FDuring a packed shift, a
OL,7,     F53-year-old chef suffers chest
OL,8,     Fpains, an 84-year-old has had a
OL,9,     Ffall on an escalator, and a
OL,10,     Ffarmer's been crushed by a bull
OL,11,     Ffrom his herd.
OL,12,G2000 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,13,     FWith appointments lasting just 10
OL,14,     Fminutes, our GPs have the
OL,15,     Fdifficult task of deciding what to
OL,16,     Fprioritise and what can safely
OL,17,     Fwait for another day.
